### Tasks Executed
- **MCP Documentation Optimization**: 
  - Refined `WebDriver` KDoc to serve as efficient MCP tool descriptions (concise first paragraph, `#mcp` tagging).
  - Updated `SourceCodeToToolCallSpec` logic to prioritize `#mcp` tagged paragraphs or default to the first paragraph for tool descriptions.
  - Implemented full KDoc extraction into `ToolSpec.help` while keeping `ToolSpec.description` concise.
